{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Marble Champions is a thrilling marble racing game that will put your skills and reflexes to the ultimate test. Navigate through intricate tracks, overcome obstacles, and rely on your skills to triumph over your rivals. As you advance through the game, you'll discover a trove of unique marbles, each with its distinctive appearance and stats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in a variety of exciting game modes, from daily time trials and tournaments to intense arena battles where you'll engage in various mini-games. Test your skills in diverse racing events like Obstacle Run, Balance Run, Downhill Dash, Cannonball Run, Survival, and Drag Races. Don't feel like racing? You can also set up your own marble races, sit back, relax, and watch some marbles roll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715940/extras/title_collect_copy_2.jpg?t=1738683951\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715940/extras/intro_gif.gif?t=1738683951\" />Climb from Rookie to Marble Champion as you face new challenges and intense competition in each division. Master the art of precision racing and platforming across official tracks, tournaments, and user-created tracks. With the intuitive Track Designer, you can craft and share your own challenging marble races.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715940/extras/title_collect.jpg?t=1738683951\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715940/extras/rollen.gif?t=1738683951\" />Fill your bag with a wide collection of marbles, each offering unique racing characteristics. From sleek, high-speed racers to robust, obstacle-conquering juggernauts, choose the marble that matches your racing style and strategy for each thrilling event.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715940/extras/title_collect_copy.jpg?t=1738683951\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715940/extras/platform_finish.gif?t=1738683951\" />Prove your speed and agility in Tournaments and Daily Time Trial Challenges. Compete against players from around the world for daily supremacy on specially designed tracks. Set the fastest time to claim your spot on the global leaderboard, or challenge friends and family in local splitscreen multiplayer matches and battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715940/extras/store_footer.jpg?t=1738683951\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738683951","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715940/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738683951","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715940/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738683951","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715940/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738683951","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Stats","id":15},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Marble Champions is a thrilling marble racing game that will put your skills and reflexes to the ultimate test. Navigate thro